OL,3,CEngland and Scotland secure wins in
OL,4,CWorld Cup warm-up games
OL,6,FEngland has beaten New Zealand 1-0 in
OL,7,Fa World Cup warm-up game in Tampa,
OL,8,FFlorida.
OL,10,FHarry Kane scored England's only goal
OL,11,Fof the game - and his 79th for England
OL,12,F- shortly before the first half ended
OL,13,Fat the Raymond James Stadium,
OL,14,Ffollowing an assist from Djed Spence.
OL,16,FNew Zealand is the lowest-ranked team
OL,17,Fin the 2026 tournament.
OL,19,FScotland also defeated Bolivia 4-0 in
OL,20,Ftheir World Cup friendly in Harrison,
OL,21,FNew Jersey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
