OL,3,CEngland and Scotland secure wins in
OL,4,CWorld Cup warm-up games
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLawrence Shankland secured the team's
OL,12,Ffirst goal in just six minutes,
OL,13,Ffollowed by Scott Tominay at 23
OL,14,Fminutes.
OL,16,FChe Adams then bagged another two,
OL,17,Ffollowing assists from Ben Gannon-Doal.
OL,19,FBoth games kicked off at 9pm UK time,
OL,20,Fpreparing fans for the late night
OL,21,Fmatches to come across the World Cup.
