OL,3,CEngland and Scotland secure wins in
OL,4,CWorld Cup warm-up games
OL,6,FThe tournament will run from June 11
OL,7,Fto July 26 across the US, Canada and
OL,8,FMexico, with the majority of games
OL,9,Ftaking place at 11 different locations
OL,10,Fwithin the States.
OL,12,FIn keeping with tradition, all three
OL,13,Fhost nations automatically qualified
OL,14,Ffor the tournament.
OL,16,FEngland has been named as one of the
OL,17,Fsix teams most likely to lift the
OL,18,FWorld Cup trophy, alongside Spain,
OL,19,FFrance, Brazil, Argentina, and
OL,20,FPortugal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
