OL,3,CEngland and Scotland secure wins in
OL,4,CWorld Cup warm-up games
OL,6,FSaturday's friendly was Scotland's
OL,7,Ffinal match before Haiti next week,
OL,8,Fwhich will kick off at 2am.
OL,10,FEngland will play all three of their
OL,11,Fgroup games in the US, with the first
OL,12,Fmatch taking place on June 17 - but
OL,13,Fthe side will have another warm-up
OL,14,Fagainst Costa Rica on June 10.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
